'''Érica Sofia de Jesus Chissapa Bicho''' (yavutse ku ya 22 Ukuboza 1988), uzwi cyane nka '''Erica Chissapa''', ni umukinnyi wa filime akaba n'umunyamakuru [[Angola|wa Angola]] .   Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri firime''[[:en:Njinga:_Queen_of_Angola|Njinga: Queen of Angola]]'', ''Voo Directo'' and ''Jikulumessu''.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 22 Ukuboza 1988 i Huambo, mu kibaya cyo hagati cya Angola . Nyuma yaje kwimukira i Luanda afite imyaka ibiri gusa kandi abana na ba sekuruza, asize ababyeyi be na barumuna be batatu mu gihugu cye. 

== Umwuga ==
Afite imyaka 14, Erica yinjiye mu ikinamico. Mugihe yari mu myitozo yitsinda ryamakinamico i Luanda, yatumiriwe gusimbura umwe mubakinnyi bakinnye, wagombaga gufungura nyuma yiminsi itatu. Hanyuma yimukiye kuri seri ya televiziyo abitumiwe n'umukinnyi Orlando Sérgio . Ariko, ntabwo yatsinze ikizamini cyambere. Nyuma yaje gutsinda guhitamo miniseries, ariko ikibabaje nuko umusaruro wahagaritswe nyuma yimitwe ibiri yanditswe. Icyakora, yakomeje kwigaragaza mu ikinamico ya [[Angola]] hamwe nitsinda ryamakinamico 'Henriques Artes'. 

Mu 2005, yakinnye muri opera yisabune ''Sede de Viver'' anakina nka 'Kátia'. Intsinzi imaze gutsinda, yatumiwe kugira uruhare runini muri Brezil-Angola ''ikorana na Minha Terra Minha Mãe'' . Mu mwaka wa 2010, yakinnye muri filimi ya [[Porutigali|Porutugali]] - Angola ''Voo Directo'' . Muri uruhererekane, Érica yagize uruhare nka 'Weza Oliveira'. Muri 2014, yatumiriwe kujya mu ikinamico ''Jikulumessu'' n'umuririmbyi Coréon Dú . 

